Author: Pleasemakeitgoaway
Text: I agree with this, esp. the thinking it means no eating at all.  I'm still riding the wave of thinking to myself "I am still eating food so i am okay" and part of me is like ok i know that it's not but the rest of me is like no I'm normal there's nothing wrong I'm still EATING   And then i browse ED subs because i relate to them so hard...

Author: swirlturls
